      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:41:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据计划削减的合同，美国天气代理机构网站消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-weather-agency-websites-to-vanish-under-planned-contract-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家海洋和大气机构有望取消与其研究部门相关的大多数网站，以取消云网络服务合同的计划，这一举动可能会在多个实验室中陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-weather-agency-websites-to-vanish-under-planned-contract-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本总理，反对党讨论美国关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-eyes-new-budget-to-help-weather-us-tariff-impact-asahi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理Shigeru Ishiba将在周五与反对派领导人会面，讨论对美国关税的回应，该报告称日本政府正在考虑编制额外的预算，以资助企业和家庭的救济措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-eyes-new-budget-to-help-weather-us-tariff-impact-asahi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国法院罢免元总统，触发选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-awaits-court-verdict-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院因其命运不佳的戒严宣言将总统Yoon Suk Yeol撤职，这为总统竞选铺平了道路，以结束已经席卷全国几个月的领导层面的真空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-awaits-court-verdict-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:45:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
